<meta name="description" content="Free pregnancy due date calculator for India. Calculate EDD from LMP (Naegele's Rule), IVF transfer date, or ultrasound CRL. Shows current pregnancy week, days to go, trimester, Indian scan schedule, and baby size. FOGSI-aligned clinical tool."/>
<meta name="keywords" content="pregnancy due date calculator India, EDD calculator LMP, IVF due date calculator, ultrasound dating pregnancy, pregnancy week calculator, how many weeks pregnant, trimester calculator India, antenatal care India, PMMVY scheme, pregnancy scan schedule India"/>
